    ('p_beauty_001:product_parent:0', 'p_beauty_001', NULL, 'parent', 'product_parent', 0, NULL, NULL, false, 'none', '{"field":"product"}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_001","externalRef":"p_beauty_001","title":"雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露淡纹紧致保湿夜间修护抗初老精华30ml","brand":"雅诗兰黛","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"精华","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/精华","priceMin":720.0,"priceMax":1260.0,"stock":300,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_001_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"parent","chunkType":"product_parent"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_001:product_profile:0', 'p_beauty_001', 'p_beauty_001:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# 雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露淡纹紧致保湿夜间修护抗初老精华30ml
品牌：雅诗兰黛
类目：美妆护肤/精华
价格区间：720.0 ~ 1260.0
图片：1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_001_live.jpg

商品摘要：雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露（小棕瓶）是品牌经典抗初老单品，主打夜间肌底修护。核心成分含高浓度二裂酵母发酵产物溶胞物，能深入修护日间紫外线、污染造成的损伤，促进肌肤代谢；搭配透明质酸锁水保湿，猴面包树籽提取物淡纹紧致。适合25+有干纹细纹、熬夜后暗沉的抗初老人群，夜间护肤时使用效果更佳。建议每晚洁面爽肤后，取3-4滴掌心温热，轻按面部至吸收，后续搭配面霜锁养。注意开封后6个月内用完，敏感肌先做耳后测试，避免不适。', '83ad1934f695f00c004ecff74fb70c7c787958e0f7dc6cc8627a916274f85272', true, 'text', '{"field":"product_profile"}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_001","externalRef":"p_beauty_001","title":"雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露淡纹紧致保湿夜间修护抗初老精华30ml","brand":"雅诗兰黛","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"精华","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/精华","priceMin":720.0,"priceMax":1260.0,"stock":300,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_001_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"product_profile","parentId":"p_beauty_001"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_001:marketing_description:0', 'p_beauty_001', 'p_beauty_001:product_parent:0', 'child', 'marketing_description', 0, '## 营销描述

雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露（小棕瓶）是品牌经典抗初老单品，主打夜间肌底修护。核心成分含高浓度二裂酵母发酵产物溶胞物，能深入修护日间紫外线、污染造成的损伤，促进肌肤代谢；搭配透明质酸锁水保湿，猴面包树籽提取物淡纹紧致。适合25+有干纹细纹、熬夜后暗沉的抗初老人群，夜间护肤时使用效果更佳。建议每晚洁面爽肤后，取3-4滴掌心温热，轻按面部至吸收，后续搭配面霜锁养。注意开封后6个月内用完，敏感肌先做耳后测试，避免不适。', 'dfa541b2a3e97fb98f75c3ad2484582bb362b6d7c5fa1a2f3773110aa43e2789', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.marketing_description"}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_001","externalRef":"p_beauty_001","title":"雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露淡纹紧致保湿夜间修护抗初老精华30ml","brand":"雅诗兰黛","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"精华","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/精华","priceMin":720.0,"priceMax":1260.0,"stock":300,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_001_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"marketing_description","parentId":"p_beauty_001"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_001:official_faq:0', 'p_beauty_001', 'p_beauty_001:product_parent:0', 'child', 'official_faq', 0, '## 官方 FAQ

问题：这款精华的核心成分二裂酵母发酵产物溶胞物有什么作用？
回答：二裂酵母发酵产物溶胞物是这款精华的核心修护成分，它能模拟皮肤微生态，帮助修护日间紫外线、污染等外界刺激造成的肌底损伤，促进肌肤新陈代谢，增强皮肤屏障功能。同时，它还能协同其他保湿和抗初老成分，提升肌肤对营养的吸收效率，长期使用可改善皮肤稳定性、细腻度，减少干纹细纹的产生。', 'c8e8c8ba95e1de8baac8d794bb5a72fd8a4d3d01545fcc0067c71e6cd308d3aa', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.official_faq","index":0}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_001","externalRef":"p_beauty_001","title":"雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露淡纹紧致保湿夜间修护抗初老精华30ml","brand":"雅诗兰黛","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"精华","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/精华","priceMin":720.0,"priceMax":1260.0,"stock":300,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_001_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"official_faq","parentId":"p_beauty_001","question":"这款精华的核心成分二裂酵母发酵产物溶胞物有什么作用？"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_001:official_faq:1', 'p_beauty_001', 'p_beauty_001:product_parent:0', 'child', 'official_faq', 1, '## 官方 FAQ

问题：不同规格的小棕瓶怎么选？30ml、50ml、75ml各适合什么情况？
回答：不同规格的选择可根据使用需求和频率：30ml经典装适合初次尝试或短期出差携带，小巧便携；50ml加大装性价比更高，单毫升价格比30ml更划算，适合日常长期使用的用户；75ml家用装容量大更实惠，适合对产品效果认可的老用户囤货，或家庭多人共用，能满足较长时间的使用需求。', '35b0aece6dbe400f388b86351a609d5c9aa9fcb1cff836831ad405e6cba7a79a', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.official_faq","index":1}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_001","externalRef":"p_beauty_001","title":"雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露淡纹紧致保湿夜间修护抗初老精华30ml","brand":"雅诗兰黛","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"精华","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/精华","priceMin":720.0,"priceMax":1260.0,"stock":300,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_001_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"official_faq","parentId":"p_beauty_001","question":"不同规格的小棕瓶怎么选？30ml、50ml、75ml各适合什么情况？"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_001:official_faq:2', 'p_beauty_001', 'p_beauty_001:product_parent:0', 'child', 'official_faq', 2, '## 官方 FAQ

问题：这款精华适合敏感肌吗？使用前需要注意什么？
回答：这款精华大部分肤质适用，但敏感肌需谨慎。因含活性修护成分，建议敏感肌使用前取少量精华涂抹于耳后或手臂内侧，观察24小时无红肿、刺痛等不适再使用。此外，开封后建议6个月内用完，避免成分失活影响效果；存放时需远离阳光直射和高温环境，保持成分活性。', 'fa07157628c379757f27e1f7eab8191cad238aaa0a9b808f7cbdeb64ac31aae6', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.official_faq","index":2}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_001","externalRef":"p_beauty_001","title":"雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露淡纹紧致保湿夜间修护抗初老精华30ml","brand":"雅诗兰黛","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"精华","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/精华","priceMin":720.0,"priceMax":1260.0,"stock":300,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_001_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"official_faq","parentId":"p_beauty_001","question":"这款精华适合敏感肌吗？使用前需要注意什么？"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_001:user_review:0', 'p_beauty_001', 'p_beauty_001:product_parent:0', 'child', 'user_review', 0, '## 用户评价

用户：李小米
评分：1
内容：用了两次就脸颊泛红刺痛，我是敏感肌平时用其他精华都没事，这款成分可能太刺激了。虽然包装是正品，但真的不适合敏感肌，早知道先做测试，现在只能闲置，浪费720块，太心疼了。', '7f3c10bfd45cdb972c677b88ff8a1fcc04b67bcb1e409fc2a97e14115ed02697', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.user_reviews","index":0}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_001","externalRef":"p_beauty_001","title":"雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露淡纹紧致保湿夜间修护抗初老精华30ml","brand":"雅诗兰黛","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"精华","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/精华","priceMin":720.0,"priceMax":1260.0,"stock":300,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_001_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"user_review","parentId":"p_beauty_001","rating":1,"sentiment":"negative"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_001:user_review:1', 'p_beauty_001', 'p_beauty_001:product_parent:0', 'child', 'user_review', 1, '## 用户评价

用户：王梓涵
评分：2
内容：用了快一个月，保湿还行，但淡纹紧致完全没效果。我26岁有轻微干纹，每晚都用，干纹还是在，720块30ml性价比太低，不会再回购了。', 'aaf1e83695e49738ed6674e4c5ea9b5c523f7bee5180652d573c2af709157c6d', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.user_reviews","index":1}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_001","externalRef":"p_beauty_001","title":"雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露淡纹紧致保湿夜间修护抗初老精华30ml","brand":"雅诗兰黛","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"精华","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/精华","priceMin":720.0,"priceMax":1260.0,"stock":300,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_001_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"user_review","parentId":"p_beauty_001","rating":2,"sentiment":"negative"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_001:user_review:2', 'p_beauty_001', 'p_beauty_001:product_parent:0', 'child', 'user_review', 2, '## 用户评价

用户：张雅静
评分：5
内容：熬夜党救星！每晚3滴吸收超快不黏腻，第二天皮肤不暗沉。半个月后眼角干纹淡了，皮肤也紧致些，已经回购50ml加大装，太爱这款精华了！', '4449b72eceebae9bcf9e99b33bc0201b5f64f82f4b652a10d4a9d2c5ccf4eba9', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.user_reviews","index":2}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_001","externalRef":"p_beauty_001","title":"雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露淡纹紧致保湿夜间修护抗初老精华30ml","brand":"雅诗兰黛","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"精华","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/精华","priceMin":720.0,"priceMax":1260.0,"stock":300,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_001_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"user_review","parentId":"p_beauty_001","rating":5,"sentiment":"positive"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_001:user_review:3', 'p_beauty_001', 'p_beauty_001:product_parent:0', 'child', 'user_review', 3, '## 用户评价

用户：刘梦琪
评分：2
内容：包装设计有问题，瓶口总残留精华，倒的时候会滴外面浪费。用了三周除了保湿没别的效果，抗初老根本没感觉，价格还贵，有点失望。', '420684f0a7b86f53b0a63607e2bc1ec427fe31bd3a812f8175fa4c0350cd864a', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.user_reviews","index":3}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_001","externalRef":"p_beauty_001","title":"雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露淡纹紧致保湿夜间修护抗初老精华30ml","brand":"雅诗兰黛","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"精华","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/精华","priceMin":720.0,"priceMax":1260.0,"stock":300,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_001_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"user_review","parentId":"p_beauty_001","rating":2,"sentiment":"negative"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_001:user_review:4', 'p_beauty_001', 'p_beauty_001:product_parent:0', 'child', 'user_review', 4, '## 用户评价

用户：陈宇飞
评分：1
内容：混油皮用了反而更干，还冒闭口。想抗初老结果皮肤状态更差，这款可能不适合混油皮，后悔买了，以后不会再试雅诗兰黛小棕瓶了。', '4eed65bf983bf4e5de6061efc296bcb8e782af6b04837976d345094c4e701c7b', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.user_reviews","index":4}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_001","externalRef":"p_beauty_001","title":"雅诗兰黛特润修护肌活精华露淡纹紧致保湿夜间修护抗初老精华30ml","brand":"雅诗兰黛","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"精华","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/精华","priceMin":720.0,"priceMax":1260.0,"stock":300,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_001_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"user_review","parentId":"p_beauty_001","rating":1,"sentiment":"negative"}'::jsonb),
