    ('p_beauty_008:product_profile:0', 'p_beauty_008', 'p_beauty_008:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# 玉兰油新生塑颜金纯面霜紧致提拉淡纹保湿抗初老大红瓶50g
