    ('p_beauty_013:product_profile:0', 'p_beauty_013', 'p_beauty_013:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# 方里柔焦蜜粉饼控油定妆细腻粉质隐匿毛孔提亮肤色粉饼7g
