    ('p_beauty_018:product_profile:0', 'p_beauty_018', 'p_beauty_018:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# The Ordinary烟酰胺10%锌1%精华液平衡油脂淡化毛孔提亮肤色30ml
