    ('p_beauty_021:product_profile:0', 'p_beauty_021', 'p_beauty_021:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# 科颜氏牛油果保湿眼霜滋润补水细腻质地淡化干纹眼周护理28g
