    ('p_beauty_022:product_profile:0', 'p_beauty_022', 'p_beauty_022:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# 薇诺娜极润保湿面膜密集补水舒缓修护肌肤屏障涂抹式面膜75g
