商品摘要：薇诺娜极润保湿面膜专为干敏肌设计，核心成分含云南高原青刺果油与马齿苋提取物，能密集补水同时舒缓泛红。75g涂抹式包装适合夜间厚敷，25g*5片装便携适合出差。使用时取适量均匀涂于面部，避开眼唇，15-20分钟后洗净。注意开封后6个月内用完，敏感肌首次使用建议先做耳后测试。', 'e39179cb0123818e7206fe87d28076c2be563ee813cb44647d530604c29e8722', true, 'text', '{"field":"product_profile"}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_022","externalRef":"p_beauty_022","title":"薇诺娜极润保湿面膜密集补水舒缓修护肌肤屏障涂抹式面膜75g","brand":"薇诺娜","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"面膜","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/面膜","priceMin":168.0,"priceMax":199.0,"stock":200,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_022_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"product_profile","parentId":"p_beauty_022"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_022:marketing_description:0', 'p_beauty_022', 'p_beauty_022:product_parent:0', 'child', 'marketing_description', 0, '## 营销描述

薇诺娜极润保湿面膜专为干敏肌设计，核心成分含云南高原青刺果油与马齿苋提取物，能密集补水同时舒缓泛红。75g涂抹式包装适合夜间厚敷，25g*5片装便携适合出差。使用时取适量均匀涂于面部，避开眼唇，15-20分钟后洗净。注意开封后6个月内用完，敏感肌首次使用建议先做耳后测试。', '4d604f8899c83bb1145c8bd6bf10501839be7eb8d6ee1e750fb1488620df9355', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.marketing_description"}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_022","externalRef":"p_beauty_022","title":"薇诺娜极润保湿面膜密集补水舒缓修护肌肤屏障涂抹式面膜75g","brand":"薇诺娜","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"面膜","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/面膜","priceMin":168.0,"priceMax":199.0,"stock":200,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_022_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"marketing_description","parentId":"p_beauty_022"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_022:official_faq:0', 'p_beauty_022', 'p_beauty_022:product_parent:0', 'child', 'official_faq', 0, '## 官方 FAQ

问题：这款面膜适合什么肤质？
回答：主要针对干性、敏感性肌肤，尤其是换季或空调房导致的肌肤干燥、泛红问题。成分温和无酒精，敏感肌可放心使用，但首次使用建议先做局部测试。', 'b3a8f31e1625478d1facd4fd1ac2b5816d0cc6872e21ae762b00b25ed7e405ec', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.official_faq","index":0}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_022","externalRef":"p_beauty_022","title":"薇诺娜极润保湿面膜密集补水舒缓修护肌肤屏障涂抹式面膜75g","brand":"薇诺娜","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"面膜","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/面膜","priceMin":168.0,"priceMax":199.0,"stock":200,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_022_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"official_faq","parentId":"p_beauty_022","question":"这款面膜适合什么肤质？"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_022:official_faq:1', 'p_beauty_022', 'p_beauty_022:product_parent:0', 'child', 'official_faq', 1, '## 官方 FAQ

问题：75g和25g*5片装的区别是什么？
回答：75g是罐装涂抹式，适合长期居家使用，单次用量更灵活；25g*5片是独立包装，方便携带，适合出差或旅行。两者成分相同，仅规格和包装形式不同。', '733d8fc9aed648f015390b7f485d6988d5de09413c0b41d2c662417ed9d637cb', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.official_faq","index":1}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_022","externalRef":"p_beauty_022","title":"薇诺娜极润保湿面膜密集补水舒缓修护肌肤屏障涂抹式面膜75g","brand":"薇诺娜","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"面膜","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/面膜","priceMin":168.0,"priceMax":199.0,"stock":200,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_022_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"official_faq","parentId":"p_beauty_022","question":"75g和25g*5片装的区别是什么？"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_022:official_faq:2', 'p_beauty_022', 'p_beauty_022:product_parent:0', 'child', 'official_faq', 2, '## 官方 FAQ

问题：使用频率建议是怎样的？
回答：干性肌肤每周2-3次，敏感肌每周1-2次。干燥季节可增加至每周3-4次，每次厚敷15-20分钟，后续无需清洗，直接进行基础护肤即可。', '614d386eb144e1e3810d89d4a6080f92aa4e146859ea26e11ba5f0bcafb2da60', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.official_faq","index":2}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_022","externalRef":"p_beauty_022","title":"薇诺娜极润保湿面膜密集补水舒缓修护肌肤屏障涂抹式面膜75g","brand":"薇诺娜","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"面膜","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/面膜","priceMin":168.0,"priceMax":199.0,"stock":200,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_022_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"official_faq","parentId":"p_beauty_022","question":"使用频率建议是怎样的？"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_022:official_faq:3', 'p_beauty_022', 'p_beauty_022:product_parent:0', 'child', 'official_faq', 3, '## 官方 FAQ

问题：开封后保质期是多久？
回答：罐装75g开封后建议6个月内用完，单片装开封后需立即使用。储存时避免阳光直射，放置于阴凉干燥处，防止成分变质影响效果。', '575c94fb6541a03e115b6c246db2cb79a7cf55f996a3bf4ea8d89adb9f6e1bb3', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.official_faq","index":3}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_022","externalRef":"p_beauty_022","title":"薇诺娜极润保湿面膜密集补水舒缓修护肌肤屏障涂抹式面膜75g","brand":"薇诺娜","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"面膜","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/面膜","priceMin":168.0,"priceMax":199.0,"stock":200,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_022_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"official_faq","parentId":"p_beauty_022","question":"开封后保质期是多久？"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_022:official_faq:4', 'p_beauty_022', 'p_beauty_022:product_parent:0', 'child', 'official_faq', 4, '## 官方 FAQ

问题：可以和其他护肤品叠加使用吗？
回答：可以。建议在洁面后直接使用面膜，后续搭配薇诺娜特护霜或保湿乳液锁水。避免与含酸类产品（如刷酸）同时使用，以免刺激肌肤。', 'aa82b6972ade063349237ca1091435e466d2797aac4cccf1d944d9ea48dae97f', true, 'text', '{"field":"rag_knowledge.official_faq","index":4}'::jsonb, '{"productId":"p_beauty_022","externalRef":"p_beauty_022","title":"薇诺娜极润保湿面膜密集补水舒缓修护肌肤屏障涂抹式面膜75g","brand":"薇诺娜","category":"美妆护肤","subCategory":"面膜","categoryPath":"美妆护肤/面膜","priceMin":168.0,"priceMax":199.0,"stock":200,"imagePath":"1_美妆护肤/images/p_beauty_022_live.jpg","chunkLevel":"child","chunkType":"official_faq","parentId":"p_beauty_022","question":"可以和其他护肤品叠加使用吗？"}'::jsonb),
    ('p_beauty_022:official_faq:5', 'p_beauty_022', 'p_beauty_022:product_parent:0', 'child', 'official_faq', 5, '## 官方 FAQ

