    ('p_beauty_023:product_profile:0', 'p_beauty_023', 'p_beauty_023:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# 理肤泉特护清盈防晒乳高倍防晒清爽控油易敏肌适用面部防晒50ml
