    ('p_beauty_024:product_profile:0', 'p_beauty_024', 'p_beauty_024:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# 珀莱雅赋能鲜颜淡纹紧致精华液抗皱紧致提升弹润淡化细纹30ml
