    ('p_digital_016:product_profile:0', 'p_digital_016', 'p_digital_016:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# OPPO Reno 16 Pro 轻薄人像摄影高刷屏快充5G智能手机12+256GB
