    ('p_digital_022:product_profile:0', 'p_digital_022', 'p_digital_022:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# 联想 ThinkPad X1 Carbon Aura AI 元启版2026 14英寸高端商务轻薄本
