    ('p_clothes_007:product_profile:0', 'p_clothes_007', 'p_clothes_007:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 41 男子缓震跑步鞋日常训练公路跑鞋
