    ('p_clothes_008:product_profile:0', 'p_clothes_008', 'p_clothes_008:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# adidas Ultraboost 5 男子缓震跑步鞋针织鞋面日常慢跑训练鞋
