    ('p_clothes_009:product_profile:0', 'p_clothes_009', 'p_clothes_009:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# HOKA Clifton 9 男子缓震公路跑鞋厚底回弹日常长距离训练鞋
