    ('p_clothes_010:product_profile:0', 'p_clothes_010', 'p_clothes_010:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# 特步 160X 6.0 PRO 碳板竞速跑鞋马拉松训练比赛轻量跑步鞋
