    ('p_clothes_011:product_profile:0', 'p_clothes_011', 'p_clothes_011:product_parent:0', 'child', 'product_profile', 0, '# Nike LeBron XXI EP 男子中帮实战篮球鞋全掌缓震室内外场地训练鞋
